{"tid":1845150,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙古關閉接壤中國邊境","createTime":"2020-01-27T03:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T09:44:57.000Z","uid":81228,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80949b548cb80c6db40560c4efabbadafba52665","tid":1845150,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200127/photo/bkn-20200127112928504-0127_00912_001_01b.jpg?20200127113751\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200127112928504-0127_00912_001_01b.jpg%3F20200127113751&h=e09d8fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒙古政府內閣舉行會議，商討應對武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續由中國擴散開去，鄰國蒙古政府宣布，周一（27日）起關閉接壤中國的邊境關卡，同時下令全國所有大學、高等教育機構及職業訓練中心關閉至3月2日，又禁止所有類型的公共集會，防止武漢肺炎疫情擴散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200127/bkn-20200127112928504-0127_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200127%2Fbkn-20200127112928504-0127_00912_001.html&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=767b5b7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200127/bkn-20200127112928504-0127_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1385906d0b9691be04572f7a58800db6f409cfd8","tid":1845150,"uid":18517,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"蒙古牛逼！"},{"pid":"0fb68a04a7d375268e2642e6a4ad8229938ea8a0","tid":1845150,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"蒙古獨立"},{"pid":"309c155789c3739c08d43d4390ea7e8506cffdb6","tid":1845150,"uid":167289,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"0fb68a04a7d375268e2642e6a4ad8229938ea8a0","tid":1845150,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"蒙古獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"獨立咗好耐"},{"pid":"efe21e21